Former president Jacob Zuma has given his baby mama Sonono Khoza just about exclusive powers over their love child. Zuma has given Khoza the right to remove the child from the Republic of South Africa without his consent. He has also given her the right to travel with the child out of the country whenever she chooses, and the right to apply for a passport and international visa or permit for their child without his consent. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD